pg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-269\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx3.jpg\" alt=\"cpx3\" width=\"522\" height=\"292\" /></a>\r\n</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Επιλέγω Ακύρωση</span></strong></strong><a href=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-270\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx4.jpg\" alt=\"cpx4\" width=\"785\" height=\"346\" />\r\n</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Λάθος Παραγγελία</strong> και <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">ΝΑΙ</span>\r\n<a href=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-271\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx5.jpg\" alt=\"cpx5\" width=\"837\" height=\"203\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>Αν δουμε αυτό το μήνυμα, η διαδικασία έχει ολοκληρωθεί.\r\n<a href=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx6.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-272\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx6.png\" alt=\"cpx6\" width=\"471\" height=\"159\" /></a></li>\r\n	<li>Στο Reporting Tool (Portal by Γκεζερλής) το περνάμε ως\r\n<strong>Αυτόματη Διεκπεραίωση</strong> - κατάστημα.\r\n<a href=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx7.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-273\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx7.png\" alt=\"cpx7\" width=\"303\" height=\"519\" /></a> <a href=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx8.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-274\" src=\"http://172.16.119.220/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cpx8.png\" alt=\"cpx8\" width=\"241\" height=\"152\" /></a></li>\r\n</ol>','Διαδικασία capex μέσω καταστήματος','','publish','open','closed','','diadikasia-capex-meso-katastimatos','','','2016-03-09 16:32